Utterance.UttText: Thuy liu, 29 years old under Dr Gregor, bed eight, came in with chest pain and found to have blood clot in her lungs.
She is self caring and ambulant.
Still awaiting for doctors to review.
And awaiting plan for her and they said they will see her later. otherwise, her obs are all normal and she had regular paracetamol and endone for pain.
